\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}6 thick-cut slices smoked bacon\
{\listtext	\'95	}4 slices good white bread, cut 1/2-inch thick\
{\listtext	\'95	}4 tablespoons good mayonnaise (recommended: Hellman's)\
{\listtext	\'95	}4 to 8 tender green {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/lettuce/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 lettuce}} leaves, washed and spun very dry\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 ripe Hass {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/avocado/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 avocado}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 lemon, juiced\
